Hilltop Holdings (HTH) Misses Q1 Earnings, Revenue Estimates
Hilltop Holdings Inc. (HTH) recorded a negative earnings surprise of 20.6% in the first quarter of 2017. The company's earnings per share of 27 cents lagged the Zacks Consensus Estimate of 34 cents and declined 3.6% year over year.

